173
0:26:23,800 --> 0:26:27,280
这头鲸将尸沉深海
It will sink into the depths below.

174
0:26:30,560 --> 0:26:34,040
而这条补充了脂肪储备的大青鲨
The blue, with its reserves of fat replenished,

175
0:26:34,040 --> 0:26:37,680
可以两个月不再进食了
Can now survive for another two months without eating.

176
0:27:00,840 --> 0:27:04,020
深海中一半以上的生物
Over half of all animals in the

177
0:27:04,020 --> 0:27:07,000
都随洋流前进
open ocean drift in currents

