184
0:28:23,720 --> 0:28:26,520
这是一个明智之举
It's such a successful strategy

185
0:28:26,520 --> 0:28:28,740
腔肠动物是地球上
That jellies are one of the most

186
0:28:28,740 --> 0:28:30,960
最常见的生命形态之一
common life form on the planet

187
0:28:40,280 --> 0:28:44,400
不过腔肠动物中 有种和水母很像
But among the jellies, and looking somewhat like them,

