They, too, it seems, have come here to breed.

243
0:35:32,360 --> 0:35:36,200
鲸鲨受到了特别的欢迎
The whale shark receives an extraordinary welcome.

244
0:35:56,120 --> 0:36:00,360
丝鲨 有三米之长
Silky sharks, themselves three metres long,

245
