..perhaps to scrape off any parasites they might have.

247
0:36:13,680 --> 0:36:17,360
这些鲨鱼对于任何新生鱼崽都是一种威胁
These sharks could be a danger to any newly born young.

248
0:36:20,960 --> 0:36:24,440
所以可能为了避开它们
So, perhaps to avoid them,

249
0:36:24,440 --> 0:36:26,640
