在那里产下它的孩子
And there she may release her young.

252
0:37:04,250 --> 0:37:05,960
在深海里
In these great depths,

253
0:37:05,960 --> 0:37:09,120
远离那些在上层水域掠食的捕食者
Away from the predators that hunt in the waters above,

254
