Her babies could grow and eventually disperse.

256
0:37:25,320 --> 0:37:27,320
没有人
No-one, it is true,

257
0:37:27,320 --> 0:37:31,040
在这人迹罕至的深海里见到过小鲸鲨
Has ever seen young ones in these little-visited depths.

258
0:37:36,480 --> 0:37:41,800
但事实上 每年都会有成千上万只待产的鲸鲨来到这里
But the fact that hundreds of expectant whale sharks come here every year

259
0:37:42,800 --> 0:37:45,880
有确凿的证据表明
Is strong evidence that somewhere here

260
0:37:45,880 --> 0:37:50,680
这儿的某处是海里最大的育儿室
Lies the nursery of the biggest fish in the sea.

261
0:38:16,880 --> 0:38:20,600
世界上有近3万座大规模岛屿
There are almost 30,000 sizeable islands

262
0:38:20,600 --> 0:38:22,560
散布在海洋里
Scattered across the world's oceans.

263
0:38:26,280 --> 0:38:28,560
其中一个是南乔治亚岛
One of them is south georgia...

264
0:38:32,990 --> 0:38:35,920
对于那些为了繁殖被迫降落的海洋居民来说
..an ideal place for those ocean dwellers

