直到到250米深的地方
We're down at 250 metres,

390
0:51:49,920 --> 0:51:52,760
这是电缆能延伸到的最远距离了
Which means we've gone to almost the end of the cable

391
0:51:52,760 --> 0:51:55,240
没有东西爆炸飞所以我们继续工作
And nothing's blown up so we're back in business.

392
0:51:57,720 --> 0:51:59,840
但是这儿什么都没有
But there's almost nothing there,

393
0:51:59,840 --> 0:52:01,800
只有很薄一层的浮游生物
Just a thick layer of plankton.

394
0:52:06,880 --> 0:52:08,400
在接下来的三个星期里
Over the next three weeks,

395
0:52:08,400 --> 0:52:11,040
他们一只灯鱼都没发现
They don't find a single lanternfish.

396
0:52:18,880 --> 0:52:20,800
这次拍摄是我们对海洋
This trip is the perfect illustration

397
0:52:20,800 --> 0:52:22,680
知之甚少的完美例证
Of why we know so little about the ocean

398
0:52:22,680 --> 0:52:24,160
我们出来找东西
We came out looking for something,

399
0:52:24,300 --> 0:52:25,640
我们不停地搜寻 搜寻 搜寻
We've searched and searched and searched,

